  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00001",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "莫怀古上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00002",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "恼恨奸贼理不该，苦苦害我为哪般。莫成替我把命染，思想起来泪涟涟。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00003",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "在下莫怀古，钱塘人氏。只因那年，进京求取功名，多亏严府提拔，官居太常寺正卿之职。恼恨汤勤，搬动是非。是我弃官逃走，被严府校卫，将我拿获，解到蓟州。幸喜莫成，替我丧命，是我逃在河北避难。昨日戚贤弟有书到来，叫我前去。看前面已是蓟州，不免马上加鞭。",
      "text_length": 122
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00004",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "一日离家一日深，莫怀古在马上自己思忖：我心中只把那汤勤来恨，大不该害得我一家离分。多亏了小莫成替我丧命，有雪艳刺汤勤才把冤伸。我这里紧加鞭催马前进，",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00005",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "远远望见蓟州城。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00006",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "莫怀古下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00007",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "傅氏上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00008",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "身居店房，远离家乡。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00009",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "老爷当年去求官，被人陷害丧黄泉。不嫌千里路途远，要到蓟州走一番。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00010",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "老身傅氏。老爷莫怀古，官居太常寺卿之职；不料被人陷害，命染黄泉，埋葬在蓟州西门以外，柳林之内。是我带领文禄，前去坟茔祭奠。前面离蓟州不远，看天色不早，正好趱路。文禄哪里？",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00011",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "莫文禄上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00012",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "忽听一声唤，急忙到跟前。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00013",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "参见奶奶！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00014",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "文禄，你看天色不早，就此趱路。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00015",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00016",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "走呀——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00017",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "有傅氏带文禄忙把路上，思想起当年事好不悲伤。叹儿夫在京都求官得赏，官居着太常卿身列朝堂。到后来遭不幸一旦命丧，落下了我一人好不凄凉。将身儿来至在柳林观望，又只见一坟茔细看端详。",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00018",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "“太常寺卿莫公之墓”。哎呀老爷呀！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00019",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "见坟茔不由人泪双抛，叫一声老爷听根苗：实指望在朝居官好，又谁知中途无下梢。可怜我千里迢迢把你寻找，老爷呀——",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00020",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "我心中好一似万把钢刀。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00021",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "莫怀古上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00022",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "催马加鞭到柳林，不知坟茔何处存。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00023",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是柳林，不知莫成坟茔，现在哪里？待我下马找寻找寻。“太常寺卿莫公之墓”。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00024",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "莫成！掌家！莫成呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00025",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "见孤坟好叫人珠泪双掉，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00026",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "不由得一阵阵哭嚎陶。可怜你为我把命丧了，万古流芳美名标。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00027",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "呀！你是何人，来在我家坟茔啼哭呀？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00028",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "此乃是我家坟茔，怎么说是你家的呀？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00029",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "分明是我家的坟茔么！你怎么前来冒认？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00030",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "且住。看此人讲话，好似我妻傅氏。待我向前冒叫一声。呀！你莫非是傅氏么？",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00031",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "呀！你是我何人，敢叫我“傅氏”？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00032",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "为丈夫莫怀古在此。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00033",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "打鬼！打鬼！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00034",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "何言“打鬼”？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00035",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "我丈夫已死多年，岂不是鬼？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00036",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "贤妻休得害怕，为丈夫并不曾死。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00037",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "我家老爷，有两处贵相。你可有么？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00038",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "什么贵相？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00039",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "我家老爷，脑后有一肉枕，又有三台骨。我若一摸，便知分晓。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00040",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "我今现有。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00041",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "待我摸来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00042",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "老爷！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00043",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "夫人！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00044",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "我夫！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00045",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "贤妻呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00046",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "老爷呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00047",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "一见老爷来到了，不由妾身泪滔滔。回头便把老爷叫，妾身言来听根苗：雪艳妹子哪里去了？",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00048",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "蓟州堂上一旦抛。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00049",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "问声莫成今何在？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00050",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "他替我一命赴阴曹。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00051",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "问老爷如今往哪里去？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00052",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "戚贤弟有书把我邀。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00053",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "如此一同齐就道，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00054",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "同到蓟州走一遭。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00055",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "这是何人？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00056",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "这就是文禄。来，见过你家爷爷。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00057",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "参见爷爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00058",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00059",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "我家爹爹，哪里去了？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00060",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "你家爷爷，骑马先行；你的爹爹，挑负行李，尚在后面。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00061",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "待我看来。怎么还不见到来？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00062",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "你当真要你家爹爹么？你随我来——这坟茔之中，就是你家爹爹！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00063",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！爹爹呀！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00064",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "听说爹爹命丧了，眼望坟茔泪双抛。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00065",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "老爷，妾身欲将文禄孩儿，认在你我的名下，作为螟蛉义子。不知老爷，意下如何？",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00066",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "夫人前去问来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00067",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "文禄，我欲将你，认在我二老的名下，作一螟蛉。不知你意如何？",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00068",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫文禄"
      ],
      "text": "如此爹娘请上，受儿一拜！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00069",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古",
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "不须拜了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00070",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "莫怀古"
      ],
      "text": "夫人，你看前面，已是蓟州，你我就此前往。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00071",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "傅氏"
      ],
      "text": "但凭老爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014008_e00072",
      "play_id": "01014008",
      "scene_id": "01014008_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
